==Latin==

===Etymology===
From ''e-'' (''out'') + ''[[repere]]'' (''to crawl'', ''to creep'').

===Verb===
'''erepere'''
# To [[crawl]] out, to [[creep]] out.

===Usage notes===
The word '''erepere''' is a [[palindrome]].

===Related Terms===
*[[repere]]

